#: ../../static_analysis.md:10
msgid "Static code analysis is a process of debugging code by examining it without executing it."
msgstr ""

#: ../../static_analysis.md:12
msgid "The `Solidity Analyzers` plugin combines three analysis tools to perform static analysis on Solidity smart contracts. Each tool checks for security vulnerabilities and bad development practices, among other issues. The plugin can be activated from the Remix `Plugin Manager`."
msgstr ""

